OL,3,CTories would give Aberdeen oil
OL,4,Cindustry 'kiss of life' says Badenoch
OL,6,FA Scottish Conservative win in
OL,7,FAberdeen South could give the oil and
OL,8,Fgas industry "the kiss of life", Kemi
OL,9,FBadenoch has said.
OL,11,FThe Conservative leader is visiting
OL,12,Fthe constituency on Tuesday ahead of
OL,13,FThursday's by-election.
OL,15,FMs Badenoch has been vocal that the
OL,16,Fparty is pro-drilling in the North Sea
OL,17,Fand said voting for the Tories would
OL,18,F"revitalise" the industry.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@_O]zD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
