FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781576262
OL,3,CTories would give Aberdeen oil
OL,4,Cindustry 'kiss of life' says Badenoch
OL,6,FShe said: "Every time I visit
OL,7,FAberdeen, people tell me that the city
OL,8,Fis on its knees because Labour and the
OL,9,FSNP are killing the oil and gas
OL,10,Findustry that is its economic
OL,11,Flifeblood.
OL,13,F"Labour's crazy ban on new drilling
OL,14,Flicences, which the SNP support, must
OL,15,Fend now. The same goes for the
OL,16,Fwindfall tax.
OL,18,F"The Conservative Party are proudly
OL,19,Fpro-drilling because it's crucial to
OL,20,Fthe north-east economy and essential
OL,21,Ffor the nation's energy security.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781576262
OL,3,CTories would give Aberdeen oil
OL,4,Cindustry 'kiss of life' says Badenoch
OL,6,F"If voters in Aberdeen South choose
OL,7,FDouglas Lumsden as their MP on
OL,8,FThursday, it will send a deafening
OL,9,Fmessage that the SNP and Labour would
OL,10,Fignore at their peril.
OL,12,F"By electing Douglas, who worked in
OL,13,Fthe sector for two decades, voters
OL,14,Fcould give the kiss of life to North
OL,15,FSea oil and gas and help revitalise
OL,16,FAberdeen."
OL,18,FScottish Conservative leader Russell
OL,19,FFindlay is set to join Ms Badenoch on
OL,20,Fher campaign visit.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
