CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781576262
OL,3,CTories would give Aberdeen oil
OL,4,Cindustry 'kiss of life' says Badenoch
OL,6,FHe said that the election is on a
OL,7,F"knife edge" between the Scottish
OL,8,FConservatives and the SNP.
OL,10,FMr Findlay said: "Thursday's by-
OL,11,Felection is a referendum on the future
OL,12,Fof North Sea oil and gas.
OL,14,F"Kemi is a champion for oil and gas
OL,15,Fworkers and the people of Aberdeen
OL,16,FSouth have the chance to elect Douglas
OL,17,FLumsden ` another great champion ` as
OL,18,Ftheir MP.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]rD@ROUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781576262
OL,3,CTories would give Aberdeen oil
OL,4,Cindustry 'kiss of life' says Badenoch
OL,6,F"This election is on a knife edge
OL,7,Fbetween the Scottish Conservatives and
OL,8,Fthe SNP so it's essential for pro-UK
OL,9,Fvoters to unite behind Douglas.
OL,11,F"If they split the vote by backing any
OL,12,Fother party, they'll end up with an
OL,13,FSNP MP who won't stand up for oil and
OL,14,Fgas jobs."
OL,16,FHowever, the SNP candidate for
OL,17,FAberdeen South, Richard Thomson, said
OL,18,Fthe Tories gave the "kiss of death" to
OL,19,Fthousands of jobs in Aberdeen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@JO]zD@UOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
