OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781576262
OL,3,CTories would give Aberdeen oil
OL,4,Cindustry 'kiss of life' says Badenoch
OL,6,FHe said: "The Tories destroyed 70,000
OL,7,Foil and gas jobs and introduced the
OL,8,Fhated windfall tax ` they have zero
OL,9,Fcredibility on our energy sector.
OL,11,F"People in Aberdeen South won't forget
OL,12,Fit was the Tories who gave the kiss of
OL,13,Fdeath to tens of thousands of jobs
OL,14,Fhere while Douglas Lumsden was asking
OL,15,Ftens of thousands of AI generated
OL,16,Fquestions on tomato sauce sachets.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOU
