OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781576262
OL,3,CTories would give Aberdeen oil
OL,4,Cindustry 'kiss of life' says Badenoch
OL,6,F"Only the SNP can and will stand up
OL,7,Ffor Aberdeen and our energy sector and
OL,8,Fby putting Scotland's energy in
OL,9,FScotland's hands we can end the
OL,10,Fwindfall tax, take sensible licensing
OL,11,Fdecisions and protect oil and gas jobs
OL,12,Fin the here and now."
OL,14,FThe UK Government has been approached
OL,15,Ffor comment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@UO]
